org.dataset_id: Unique identifier for a Dataset from the organizational perspective.
org.dataverse_id: Unique identifier for the dataverse coming from the organization. Ether dataverse ID or dataverse alias. Relates to column in datverses.csv.
org.privateurl: Private URL related to the Dataset.
org.to_upload: Is the Dataset to be uploaded.
org.to_publish: Is the Dataset to be published.
org.to_delete: Is the Dataset to be deleted.
org.to_update: Dataset Metadata is to be updated.
dv.otherId: Other identifier related to the Dataset.
dv.title: Title
dv.subtitle: Subtitle
dv.series: Series, which the Dataset is part of.
dv.author: Author(s), work creator(s) of the Dataset content.
dv.subject: Subject
